			<p class="post-month">Nov</p>
			<p class="post-day">12</p>
			<p class="post-year">2004</p>				
		</div>

		My brother Adam and some collaborators have put together 19 theses on the future of the Democratic Party. They plan to launch them in a provocative way on Monday. For those of you know don&#8217;t know, Adam is the former president of the Sierra Club and a grassroots activist who runs a group called Common Assets. The these are well worth reading for those of us looking to find a ...
		
	</div>

